Python and Flask Rest API

Pip
1.	pip install Flask
2.	pip install Flask-RESTful
3.	pip install MarkupSafe

Conda
1.	conda install -c anaconda flask
2.	conda install -c conda-forge flask-restful
3.	conda install -c anaconda markupsafe


Run Flask
1.  set FLASK_APP=hello.py
2.  set FLASK_ENV=development
3.  flask run


or
python hello.py



Change host name and debug true
app.run(debug=True, host='163.180.116.64')


post call:
curl host_url -d "task=something new" -X POST -v
curl http://163.180.116.64:5000/ -d "data_path=data/test/1.mp4" -X POST -v